3 Official short biography] at [[Naenara]]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20170729133349/http://www.korean-books.com.kp/en/search/?page=work-leader3 Kim Jong-un's works] at Publications of the DPRK\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-ppo}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Kim Jong-il]]|rows=3}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Chairman of the Workers' Party of Korea|Chairman]] of the [[Workers' Party of Korea]]<br />{{small|[[First Secretary of the Workers' Party of Korea|First Secretary]]: 2012\u20132016}}|years=2016\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc|rows=3}}\n|-\n{{s-ttl|title=Chairman of the [[Central Military Commission of the Workers' Party of Korea|Central Military Commission]]<br />{{small|Acting: 2011\u20132012}}|years=2012\u2013present}}\n|-\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Leader of the Workers' Party of Korea|Leader]] of the [[Presidium of the Politburo of the Workers' Party of Korea|Presidium of the Politburo]]<br /> of the [[Workers' Party of Korea]]<br />{{small|Acting: 2011\u20132012}}|years=2012\u2013present}}\n|-\n{{s-new|office}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Vice Chairman of the<br />[[Central Military Commission (North Korea)|Central Military Commission]]|alongside=[[Ri Yong-ho (general)|Ri Yong-ho]]|years=2010\u20132012}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Choe Ryong-hae]]<br /> & [[Ri Yong-ho (general)|Ri Yong-ho]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Kim Kyong-hui]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Director of the <br /> [[Organization and Guidance Department]]|years=2012\u20132017}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Choe Ryong-hae]]}}\n|-\n{{s-off}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Kim Jong-il]]|rows=2}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Supreme Leader of North Korea]]|years=2011\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc|rows=2}}\n|-\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Chairman of the State Affairs Commission]]<br />{{small|[[National Defence Commission]]: 2012\u20132016}}|years=2016\u2013present}}\n|-\n{{s-mil}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Kim Jong-il]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Supreme Commander of the Korean People's Army|Supreme Commander]] of the<br />[[Korean People's Army]]|years=2011\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n{{s-end}}\n{{Kim Jong-un}}\n{{Navboxes\n|titlestyle = bac